{"build_type":"library","module_name":"spin-until-ring-slot-sequence","package_name":"spin-until-ring-slot-sequence","description":"Lock-free reclaim-ring per-slot sequence wait: spin (tail-recursive) until the slot's seq word (slot[0]) equals target. Bounded because the peer producer/consumer publishes/releases the slot in a few straight-line instructions with no intervening park or syscall (obstruction-free per slot). Vyukov MPMC handshake, no CAS.","function_definitions":{"spin-until-ring-slot-sequence":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"slot","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"target","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"array_read","dest":"s","base":"slot","index":"zero","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":"==","lhs":{"value":"s"},"rhs":{"value":"target"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"zero"}}],"branch_on_failure":[]},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"spin-until-ring-slot-sequence","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"slot"},{"kind":"var","value":"target"}],"result_assignment_variable":"r","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"r"}}]}}}